  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca 1800 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0da0\u0dca\u0da0\u0dda\u0db1\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "1800 liters of diesel is caught from Valachchen",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Valachchena Police say that 1800 liters of diesel taken from the Valachchena Fisherman's Harbor fuel station were prepared to be transported to Katthankudi by a lorry and a van and seven persons were arrested with the diesel stock and the lorry early this morning.",
        "The arrested suspects are residents of Kalmunai and Kattankudi areas, Valachchena Acting Police Station Sub-Inspector RM Kumarasinghe said during our enquiry.",
        "Valachchena Police, who are conducting the investigation, states that the seized 1800 diesel was packed into eighteen buckets and packed into the van, and another 21 buckets were carefully packed and loaded into the lorry.",
        "They did not have a license to transport the seized diesel and the police suspect that it was sent ready to be transported for sale at a higher price."
      ],
